非位處地面、毗鄰可合理地供傭工安全工作的露台或走廊，則必須符合以下安全措施方可進行清潔外窗： <br />\n<br />\n一、 被清潔的窗戶須已安裝窗花，而該窗花須鎖上或被固定，以防止窗花被開啟；及 <br />\n<br />\n二、 傭工除了手臂外，身體其他部分不得伸出窗外。 <br />\n<br />\n所有於2017年1月1日或之後簽訂的合約，都必須使用已加入新條款的修訂標準僱傭合約。"},{"pid":"efc55d69962b6b50bd82e8690aebf7059ce78ac3","tid":831994,"uid":108756,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e242bc2096b018aee9a4220664bb51636306dd6","tid":831994,"uid":37431,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"3edcd0aa53813e723b5c89227c45ba140868858a","tid":831994,"uid":108756,"like":5,"dislike":26,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:55:18.000Z","msg":"認真 咁樣跌一跌跌左筆錢好無謂同唔值"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:02:51.000Z","msg":"以家講緊人命呀 屌你老母！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"但我講緊金錢損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a5ebf1bba6ff87fc0819d16c45bbeab2b08060","tid":831994,"uid":108756,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e242bc2096b018aee9a4220664bb51636306dd6","tid":831994,"uid":37431,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"3edcd0aa53813e723b5c89227c45ba140868858a","tid":831994,"uid":108756,"like":5,"dislike":26,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:55:18.000Z","msg":"認真 咁樣跌一跌跌左筆錢好無謂同唔值"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:02:51.000Z","msg":"以家講緊人命呀 屌你老母！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:19:04.000Z","msg":"所以咪話要睇實啲 一陣一個唔覺跌左落去又無左筆錢"},{"pid":"7cb226e5f6b5c093b2a0109c3079bc9c85542abf","tid":831994,"uid":65328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a985e29cf5546a1c73c58f73cd5be015afa8945a","tid":831994,"uid":74259,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"話時話 之前好興個隻磁石抹窗舊野唔見哂咁ge"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"因為d人識淘寶買， 而且新樓既玻璃窗好厚， 要用勁d貴d先唔會跌"},{"pid":"6686186cf9c5417fee8229d9cf8835871dba8c82","tid":831994,"uid":36142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma