,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:59:00.000Z","msg":"諗起子華棟篤笑一幕<br />\n你企出去抹，係囉，企出去抹"},{"pid":"d55a10f9368dbd6b62f9d3fcc65552c6dba7471e","tid":831994,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:11:14.000Z","msg":"我諗個業主驚d<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f7448b30d66717023e7b90a333e2955f357928","tid":831994,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:18:11.000Z","msg":"唔識單手游出公海嘅人係會大驚小怪"},{"pid":"cd13ef692adb81e45b470598e001560bbefa3a12","tid":831994,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9f7448b30d66717023e7b90a333e2955f357928","tid":831994,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:18:11.000Z","msg":"唔識單手游出公海嘅人係會大驚小怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7430b9dc18da8e69fedc94f587ff4678d4c0b6","tid":831994,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:50:16.000Z","msg":"其實僱主犯咩法？"},{"pid":"eec8e1848e14fa3a2d731adbf5433bbba65dd285","tid":831994,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:55:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fdh.labour.gov.hk/tc/qa_cleaning_window_clause.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fdh.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fqa_cleaning_window_clause.html&d=OKT7wwAq0alXNoREpGbchMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=352ba652\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fdh.labour.gov.hk/tc/qa_cleaning_window_clause.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>問5：<br />\n如僱主在未有遵從合約所訂明的條件而要求外傭抺外窗，會有何後果？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n答5：<br />\n作為締約雙方，僱主和外傭需遵守合約上的條款。如僱主要求外傭在違反合約條文的情況下抹外窗，外傭可拒絕相關的工作要求。如有需要，外傭亦可向勞工處的勞資關係科求助。勞資關係科透過免費調停服務，協助僱主和外傭解決勞資糾紛。<br />\n<br />\n如外傭因被逼在沒有安全措施下抹外窗而要提早終止合約，與違反其他標準僱傭合約的條文一樣，受屈的外傭可向勞工處的勞資關係科求助或就其認為被變相解僱而向法庭提出補償申索(如一個月代通知金及其他終止僱傭合約的款項等)。"},{"pid":"89d8c2d3c5640ecb79db47c77868e388b5578df2","tid":831994,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:57:06.000Z","msg":"幾樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951f367369be4ef1f55aa31694bf45f102062f27","tid":831994,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 佢夠彊果下勁<br />\n<br />\n我行近少少都嚇撚死"},{"pid":"35c35480bb75fa4fefc95bed180f06189799b2a7","tid":831994,"uid":83060,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:17:50.000Z","msg":"當然唔係賓妹，賓妹而家攞正牌唔抹窗唔含撚，有時間都去遊行爭取加人工，得鳩閒同你擒高擒低。 <br />\n<br />\n呢個喺戶主嚟。"},{"pid":"2fb8bfe3f043e6edcc79b9442fff88423dad84fd","tid":831994,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:18:55.000Z","msg":"兇宅go go go"},{"pid":"ce976af158661637570f494e4a693a81ba29ab06","tid":831994,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T19:38:41.000Z","msg":"d命賤到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fd2149b275b9f1508fe950ea478c5c399aaf70","tid":831994,"uid":110997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf535a84e32b89377f02b9fc507da01eddbdf4c0","tid":831994,"uid":12618,"like":32,"dislike":7,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"好多賓妹都無安全意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T19:51:33.000Z","msg":"所以佢地好多時都唔用安全套<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70b9881e8ccb10d886f90996aadd699ec5e1029","tid":831994,"uid":130365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T21:00:43.000Z","msg":"似業主叫佢清潔埋外面 ( 用棍 之類), 唔係就咁成個行出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢跌一跌就幾百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}